{"tid":2260401,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"SM新女團「aespa」Winter是她？　11歲選秀「暴牙＋圓臉」舊照起底","createTime":"2020-10-27T14:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T17:55:30.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9b08023591d0df91b1b0e15fb518032e1fc89417","tid":2260401,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:07:56.000Z","msg":"南韓「三大經紀公司」的SM娛樂，相隔六年後即將在11月推出再次新人女團「aespa」，第一位成員Winter的概念照也在27日公開。據悉她是2001年出生，韓國人，但對於其他消息都保密到家。不過有人發現，Winter似乎就是曾在選秀節目《K-pop Star 2》出現的參賽者金敏貞（音譯）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5229/d5229641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5229%2Fd5229641.jpg&h=8ccde94d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SM新女團「aespa」首位公開成員Winter。（圖／翻攝自Twitter／aespa）<br />\nSM娛樂目前尚為公開Winter包括真實姓名等資訊，不過推特上有小道消息透露，Winter本名金敏貞（音譯），練習時間大概是3到5年，今年19歲。而根據這訊息，網友找到，在2012播出的《K-pop Star 2》，其中就有一名當年11歲的參賽者，也叫做金敏貞。<br />\n<br />\n除了年齡和姓名都對上之外，當年《K-pop Star 2》的金敏貞，和Winter五官也有幾分相似，也同樣都有深邃的雙眼皮。只是當年才11歲的金敏貞，外表還有著嬰兒肥，門牙也不太整齊，不過看得出來是個「美人底」。<br />\n<br />\n若是以參加《K-pop Star 2》後，才成為練習生的時間推算，也差不多符合「練習時間3到5年」的描述。雖然還不能確定，《K-pop Star 2》的金敏貞就是Winter，不過已經有網友表示：「其實看得出來長相沒什麼變，但想必整牙和減肥是經過一番努力的。」<br />\n<br />\nSM娛樂每每推出新人團體都引發討論，這回「aespa」也不例外。韓網更流出一張合照，畫面右邊的就是Winter，左邊則是先前疑似被爆出私人對話，使得SM娛樂大動作澄清的20歲女練習生柳智敏，中間趴著的就是「SM Rookies」企劃公開過的女練習生，唯一還留在該公司的大陸練習生寧寧，這組照片也被懷疑就是「出道組」的合照。"},{"pid":"4c00650986c222d37f6cf1209ad7ceca8dd7db49","tid":2260401,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:08:29.000Z","msg":"Cool牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06adca98dbc476adacc19feae2663b8ada964e1d","tid":2260401,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5231/d5231879.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5231%2Fd5231879.jpg&h=5048aadb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「aespa」成員Winter，疑似是《K-pop Star 2》當年11歲的參賽者金敏貞。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5231/d5231874.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5231%2Fd5231874.jpg&h=cb4dbf0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「aespa」成員Winter，疑似是《K-pop Star 2》當年11歲的參賽者金敏貞。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5231/d5231875.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5231%2Fd5231875.jpg&h=07e7bf94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金敏貞當時雖然有暴牙和嬰兒肥，但仍看得出深邃的雙眼皮，是個「美人底」。（圖／翻攝自韓網）"},{"pid":"50132a1ecc582779c820a66cd7d7c8fab3d099b8","tid":2260401,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5229/d5229642.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5229%2Fd5229642.jpg&h=0242eeae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SM新女團「aespa」首位公開成員Winter。（圖／翻攝自Twitter／aespa）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5231/d5231880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5231%2Fd5231880.jpg&h=90be7e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲韓網流傳疑似「aespa」出道組的合照，左起為柳智敏、寧寧、Winter。（圖／翻攝自韓網）"},{"pid":"e82ee50ebe3c02a74aab3766962c502cb8868493","tid":2260401,"uid":256796,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"06adca98dbc476adacc19feae2663b8ada964e1d","tid":2260401,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5231/d5231879.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5231%2Fd5231879.jpg&h=5048aadb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「aespa」成員Winter，疑似是《K-pop Star 2》當年11歲的參賽者金敏貞。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5231/d5231874.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5231%2Fd5231874.jpg&h=cb4dbf0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「aespa」成員Winter，疑似是《K-pop Star 2》當年11歲的參賽者金敏貞。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5231/d5231875.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5231%2Fd5231875.jpg&h=07e7bf94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金敏貞當時雖然有暴牙和嬰兒肥，但仍看得出深邃的雙眼皮，是個「美人底」。（圖／翻攝自韓網）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:08:58.000Z","msg":"美人底......"},{"pid":"21190951cabdc5ed934f06f395ef0dd8487c414b","tid":2260401,"uid":256796,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:09:50.000Z","msg":"樓主好鍾意po啲樣衰嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f7fc6b22180a0581af0922c818eef6708e3f34","tid":2260401,"uid":213607,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:11:28.000Z","msg":"見到打冷震=winter"},{"pid":"61edd4f37cbb95015caa4566c59af07d665b6684","tid":2260401,"uid":344625,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:11:56.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係18歲前儲錢整容架啦 有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724024a862e3b771fd44d6180223513990a2f19f","tid":2260401,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"21190951cabdc5ed934f06f395ef0dd8487c414b","tid":2260401,"uid":256796,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:09:50.000Z","msg":"樓主好鍾意po啲樣衰嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"太大路not my style<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dda9e25184b05503da9af703e766b0fc17c05f9","tid":2260401,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12f7fc6b22180a0581af0922c818eef6708e3f34","tid":2260401,"uid":213607,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:11:28.000Z","msg":"見到打冷震=winter"},"citedB